                    <span>An outstanding book.  Very well researched and a methodical investigtion of the underworld that the rap music business has become.  To the few people who thought that this book was a waste of time I can't imagine that you read the same book.  There is so much evidence that the top brass of the LAPD covered up certain investigations that it is overwhelming.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">A reader from Houston</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
